.)", "d.g. beers & co", "worley & bracher", "h.j. toudy & co", "lanagan, j."], "date": "1878", "dates": ["1878"], "description": ["Shows precinct boundaries and the names of some residents. Relief shown by contours. Includes business notices, population table, and 6 insets. Copy imperfect: Shellacked. Sectioned in 6, separated and torn along horizontal and vertical folds, each section encapsulated in mylar, and mounted on cloth backing. LC Land ownership maps, 227 Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:39:21.155Z", "group": ["gmd.mar", "catalog-split-09", "catalog", "general-maps", "main-catalog-split-09"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2012593102/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd395/g3953/g3953c/la000227.gif", "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd395/g3953/g3953c/la000227.gif#h=153&w=150", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd395:g3953:g3953c:la000227/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1843&w=1805", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd395:g3953:g3953c:la000227/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=3686&w=3610"], "index": 10, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "christian county", "kentucky"], "mime_type": ["image/gif", "image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["2022-02-18t16:32:39", "2012593102", "sheet", "2025-06-07t05:21:15.500000"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map"], "other_title": ["Map of Christian County, Kentucky"], "partof": ["geography and map division", "catalog", "county landownership maps", "cultural landscapes"], "score": 33.18446, "shelf_id": "G3953.C5G46 1878 .D4", "site": ["catalog"], "subject": ["landowners", "christian county (ky.)", "christian county", "real property", "united states", "kentucky", "cadastral maps", "maps"], "timestamp": "2026-04-29T16:06:30.250Z", "title": "Map of Christian County, Ky"